{
  "stem": "3928.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and your experience crossing paths, was there ever any-- was there ever a time when you had to do something that you didn't want to do, to prove to the SS that you were a loyal SS?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never had to do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was assigned as a liaison between the Hungarian and the German Army-- I mean, the SS and the Hungarian Army.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as such, I never had anything except convey information or gave him orders, which came in to move, where troop movements, or daily routine things, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had never, ever was told to do anything special, you know, or as far as-- I was in-- I was in my office.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I spend my time there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in-- I had my choice, as an officer, to either stay in the camp, in the Ludovica Academy, which was like a West Point, or I could go out and sleep outside.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always told them I have a girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I got to go to my girlfriend at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- they liked that very much, the idea, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they always told me there, you should have some girlfriend for us, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my steady answer was always this-- if you're man enough to want one, you should be man enough to find one.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I used to tell them  this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and I was able to get away with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's the only reason I could go out at night with my car and take my car with me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's the only reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Until one time, my car was ruined, my Mercedes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's when I changed to a DKW, which was a Audi, because my car was ruined, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
